summary: This is an email from the DOJ's voicemail system forwarding a voice message to the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York's Epstein victims contact address. The email itself contains no substantive content about the case, only metadata about the forwarded message.
keyFacts: A voice message was forwarded to the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York's Epstein victims contact address on August 7, 2019.
The email originated from the DOJ's voicemail system, indicating official communication channels were being used for victim outreach.
The actual content of the voice message is not included in this document, only the forwarding metadata.
